package week1;

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Q1 {

	public static void main(String[] args) {
		// TODO Auto-generated method stub
		Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
		int num1 = sc.nextInt();
		boolean flag = true;
		for (int i = 2; i <= Math.sqrt(num1); i++) {
			if (num1 % i == 0) {
				flag = false;
				break;
			}
		}
		if(flag) {
			System.out.println("是質數");
		}else {
			System.out.println("不是質數");
		}
	}

}
